Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就裝作是新髮型就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來 有好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是睡翹了 還是好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新上市的紅豆味果汁的百人份試飲品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡被大家圍繞著的露出燦爛笑臉的風早同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得風早同學被大家圍繞著好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想變得和風早同學一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:21:04.62,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,人員表 翻譯 瑤瑤 阿虛 時間校譯 阿虛 義工 被風早同學萌倒的諾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感情也在一步一步的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那個大學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是早晨上午還是半夜 一個勁的問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出來見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不馬上回我短信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不出來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和別的男人在一起嗎之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然是 早上醒來到學校 然後和同學一起上課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後晚上睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那矢野為什麼要和那種男生交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被搭訕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這傢伙一開始都是一副寬容成熟的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我認為和女人交往很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在覺得男人才麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這種情況 會有多方面的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被愛到覺得頭痛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的戀愛都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚上去你家 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩遊戲吧 繼續玩上次那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我們對戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千和真田同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的氣質感覺非常的相配
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對千鶴一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好 真的沒有見過比這倆人更般配的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千又怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喜歡真田同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大叔 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假我還會來店裡幫忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小千可是店裡的招牌店員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我上去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 不過說實話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千要是我家的女兒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以的話我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 我不是說了我會過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了千鶴的夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會說夢話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個獅子 幻獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍你有什麼想要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500日元以內的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的棒球手套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了500日元以內的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捶肩券以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以啦 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說要送你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 正月的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是為了那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸在洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定得和她說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 矢野 一起去買東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想盡早見到他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有空的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的生日禮物 馬上就到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個講義氣的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是對我暗送秋波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在對人家放電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也不知道人家名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽 承載我倆命運的腳步聲正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 起來 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要站起來 城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年給他買什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢 就給他捶肩券了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捶肩券?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙當場就用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整整捶了3小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真為真田同學的健康著想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的預算是500元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF6F4F4&\3c&H8B2E2F&}(棒球白癡)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真配他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說買不起新的棒球手套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是手套袋的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今年就奢侈一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逛的真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷你裙?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也想換換造型什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵 拉麵 拉麵 啦啦啦 拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想問她啊 可以問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得現在問準沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的拉麵 世界第一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小千...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 突然這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一直是單戀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我單戀了很長時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他好像只當我是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己還只是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家根本不會理我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我還是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會成為一個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要長大了就會有所改變的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問出來真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見小千有這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總是見不到面 真寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對方住在札幌嘛 這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的盂蘭盆節沒有回來 所以已經1年沒見過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正月的時候肯定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著看吧 變成高中生的本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以開門見山的問下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真田君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 你該不會是說龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是把龍當做兄弟來看待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的變成姐弟也可以的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田君知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍嗎 怎麼可能不知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音大點 真田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也給我大點聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們一起安慰城呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子啊 沒頭沒腦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢 為了鼓勵一下城我們決定出去玩下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周週末有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周我去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說有事...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有相當大的決心是穿不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 我的決心可是很強大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我長了一雙美腿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千好耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為能見到喜歡的人是件非常讓人開心的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨...好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種怎麼樣 風早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 冬裝?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 迷你裙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15000...好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在缺錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想在正月的時候穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月?那個時候不是有壓歲錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果徹只有除夕和元旦在家的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫做徹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沒說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大清早的吵什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把他甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是費了不少工夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的心情坦率的說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他要分手之後...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了綾音我一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們同居吧 綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了 這人根本沒有聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你們甜蜜的去見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到一句安慰她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初也沒有期望著這樣的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那算啥 就好像我被甩了一樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有一個被甩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失戀的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我和你相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說戀愛就伴隨著甩和被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然還是很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 是我把他甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼拒絕我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用逞強也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦啊 矢野很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒告訴吉田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太的話 會告訴她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為決定怎麼做的是她而不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的千鶴突然見到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是最糟糕的戲劇性場面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月?迷你裙?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼輕飄飄的那種...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是買適合你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 不適合我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女間的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千喜歡的男人會是什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千看起來好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野痛苦的時候 我居然一個人這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 矢野 打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 在我家搞個聚會吧 安慰下矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週末來我家過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子也會一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來玩對戰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游 遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說進來之後你再進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在換衣服怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句話原封不動的還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 你很久都沒過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃唄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 實際上...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 話還沒說...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我只是與人相處就已經手忙腳亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有時間去顧及戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以從來沒有考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是愛情一定是和友情一樣複雜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以能夠明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是因為喜歡上了風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:25.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空いっばいの紙ひこきぐらいになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:25.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:25.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:25.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飄飄浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:47.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:47.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未到達天空就破滅消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:53.46,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:53.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們想要的永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:22:01.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:22:01.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管想要永遠留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:12.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:12.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:21.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:21.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找尋到了屬於我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:34.57,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(702,365)}第19話 夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微微泛起的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色彩永遠不會褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 夢
